<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.1.6">
<l>paṇiyēy paraṅkuṉ ṟiṉpavaḷat tiraḷē</l>
<l>muṉiyē tirumū ḻikkaḷattuvi ḷakkē</l>
<l>yiṉiyāy toṇṭarōm parukiṉṉamu tāya</l>
<l>kaṉiyē yuṉṉaikkaṇ ṭukoṇṭuyntoḻin tēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Coral orb of the high snow-worthy peaks,</l>
<l>Sage, lamp in Tirumūḻikkalam, you [so] sweet,</l>
<l>Fruit which becomes the sweet nectar that we, your servants, sip,</l>
<l>Seeing you for myself [and] being saved, I was at ease.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
